{"tid":419911,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地當初點解會上高登？","createTime":"2017-10-01T02:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T07:41:24.000Z","uid":75524,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92e8cafce47144ebcff2bbf1c080f89f17087e1b","tid":419911,"uid":75524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"喺utube鳩fing 見到有堆高登音樂台片<br />\n覺得幾好笑 就想上高登睇下究竟咩黎<br />\n上到黎發覺啲鳩up文化好正 同自己不謀而合<br />\n現實世界唔講得 冇人明嘅嘢呢度都可以𣈱所欲言<br />\n而且好多同自己想法相近嘅人<br />\n慢慢咁就長駐咗呢個介乎現實同虛擬嘅烏托邦五年了<br />\n想當年我仲係小二學生 日日大把時間上高登<br />\n但係而家對住啲sin cos tan<br />\n唔好話上高登 上你老母都冇時間<br />\n所以你地要好好珍惜上連登嘅時光<br />\n如果唔係好似我咁 上到中學就冇時間上連登了～<br />\n唉唔講了 要溫書 聽日背默孔乙己<br />\n<br />\n嗚呼哀哉"},{"pid":"66df2c70f6a2c6ee7bd90bc619660fa927cd2f74","tid":419911,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"睇蘋果動話高登有post講<br />\n唔知鄧麗欣定傅穎係屎上最佳女歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1d2ac2a7efdad2698a3c98b65361139104a0d2","tid":419911,"uid":75524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇蘋果動話高登有post講<br />\n唔知鄧麗欣定傅穎係屎上最佳女歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屎塔肥幼稚園時代女神"},{"pid":"08cb6875f6a9af823ddf46074f676a3305fde2a9","tid":419911,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:31:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7cfdcc68cf25fd37fdda9fa9019dc5924fa5908","tid":419911,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"睇巴士呀叔remix"},{"pid":"b99ea3e5a037ca5cb63e44cc0dae55d6fb4fb7c2","tid":419911,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"喺Facebook留言之後拎到個高登ac"},{"pid":"402c9712da3c94bd948e6b3a13beca3b55b88e20","tid":419911,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:45:31.000Z","msg":"聽完給阿義叔<img src=\"/asse